title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - May 31 2022

description:
Buck vividly describes those who wore masks on his trip to Bermuda. The New York Times admits mask mandates don't work. Inflation will cause suffering, food shortages. Biden has no clue how to stop inflation. Lia Thomas says he didn't transition to get an edge in swimming. Men cannot become women. Buck shocked that Clay doesn't mind people blasting Bluetooth speakers on the beach. Clay ejected from Little League baseball game.
